OL,3,CFormer football chairman Ken Bates
OL,4,Cdies aged 94
OL,6,FThe former football chairman and
OL,7,Fowner, Ken Bates, has died aged 94.
OL,9,FBates was a key figure at Leeds United
OL,10,Ffor 8 years.
OL,12,FHe became owner of Leeds United in
OL,13,F2005 and was chairman for more than 8
OL,14,Fyears, until stepping down following
OL,15,Fthe sale of the club to GFH Capital in
OL,16,F2013.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
