OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1783961289
OL,3,CFormer football chairman Ken Bates
OL,4,Cdies aged 94
OL,6,FThe football club which he is most
OL,7,Fassociated with however, Chelsea FC,
OL,8,Fannounced on Saturday 11 July that he
OL,9,Fhad died peacefully in Monaco
OL,10,Fsurrounded by his wife and family.
OL,12,FIn a statement, they said: "The club
OL,13,Fsends our heartfelt condolences to
OL,14,FKen's wife Suzannah, the rest of his
OL,15,Ffamily and his friends.
OL,17,F"Colourful, outspoken and
OL,18,Fcontroversial are adjectives often
OL,19,Fused to describe Bates, and his style,
OL,20,Fviews and actions divided opinion.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
