OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1783961289
OL,3,CFormer football chairman Ken Bates
OL,4,Cdies aged 94
OL,6,F"Football club chairmen became
OL,7,Fprominent and well-known like never
OL,8,Fbefore in the latter part of the 20th
OL,9,FCentury and none more so than Ken
OL,10,FBates."
OL,12,FLeeds United also put out a comment,
OL,13,Fsaying:
OL,15,F"The thoughts of everyone at Leeds
OL,16,FUnited are with the family, friends
OL,17,Fand former colleagues of Ken at this
OL,18,Fdifficult time."
